---
title: Savoury Braised Chickpeas and Chicken Tenders with Feta and Yogurt Sauce
description: Protein-packed chickpeas and chicken get a flavour boost from warm curry paste in this hearty and fragrant stew. You'll want to scoop up every last bite of this veggie-filled wonder!
